    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a comparative, open label, parallel group, non interventional study to further
      demonstrate the effectiveness and tolerability of Ectoin® Rhinitis Nasal Spray. In addition
      the effectiveness and safety shall be compared to a Sinupret forte. The patient applies
      Ectoin® Rhinitis Nasal Spray or takes Sinupret forte according to the instructions for use.
      The observation takes place over a period of 14 days. Response to treatment is recorded at
      day 7 and day 14 by the physician and in daily by the patient in a dairy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
